# Per-user Claude Code settings
.claude/
# …except the engine test fixtures, which deliberately ship a .claude/ tree
# as ground-truth input. Without these the Vitest engine suite fails on a
# fresh checkout (CI). Re-include the dir *and* its contents (a file negation
# alone is ignored while its parent dir stays excluded).
!electron/main/engine/__fixtures__/**/.claude/
!electron/main/engine/__fixtures__/**/.claude/**

# Code-signing material — never commit
.cert/
*.key
*.pem
*.p12
*.cer

